description:
The investment seeks to track the investment results of the MSCI All Colombia Capped Index composed of Colombian equities.
 The fund generally will invest at least 90% of its assets in the component securities of the underlying index and in investments that have economic characteristics that are substantially identical to the component securities of the underlying index and may invest up to 10% of its assets in certain futures, options and swap contracts, cash and cash equivalents. The index is designed to represent the performance of the broad Colombia equity universe. The fund is non-diversified.
